# Private key of the event's utility address — the oracle signs settle() as the utility.
# For the MVP the oracle holds the key directly; post-MVP this becomes oracle-signature
# verification or a multisig (see contracts/sources/voltray.move settle()).
#
# Export it with:
#   sui keytool export --key-identity <utility-address>
# then copy the "suiprivkey1..." value below.
ORACLE_SECRET_KEY=suiprivkey1...
